```dockerfile
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve
COPY . .
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    cd /tmp/certs && \
    curl -o rds-ca-2019-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    curl -o rds-ca-2015-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2015-root.pem && \
    curl -o DigiCertGlobalRoot.crt https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRoot.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2019 -file rds-ca-2019-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2015 -file rds-ca-2015-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-global -file DigiCertGlobalRoot.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -S appgroup && adduser -S -u 1001 -G appgroup app
COPY --from=builder /app/target/app.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:appgroup /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java analytics dashboard with cloud database support"

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
